            <abstract>
                <p>Magic prayer against the demons Bāryā and Legewon and against the breath of demons using ʾasmāt, which are indicated as 
                    ‘Arabic spells’ (<foreign xml:lang="gez">qāl ʿārabi </foreign>). The prayer is similar to 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7883AyyaraAganent"/> and <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4644MagicPr"/> in 
                    <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient4943#ms_i5"/>.</p>
